Is it here?

118
00:17:37,514 --> 00:17:38,724
Here?

119
00:17:51,737 --> 00:17:52,946
That's enough for today.

120
00:18:15,677 --> 00:18:17,596
This is so good! Wow!

121
00:18:25,437 --> 00:18:26,730
This place is insane!

122
00:18:31,443 --> 00:18:33,946
God, the house feels so empty. Right?

123
