-Yeah.
-How did you know I was thirsty?

135
00:19:37,926 --> 00:19:39,136
-Thank you!
-Sure.

136
00:19:42,472 --> 00:19:43,807
That is so refreshing!

137
00:19:47,019 --> 00:19:48,812
What is it you need help with?

138
00:19:51,315 --> 00:19:53,317
It's our department fashion show.

139
00:19:53,817 --> 00:19:56,570
No need to get on stage,
but could you help me with the fitting?

140
00:19:56,653 --> 00:19:59,156
I'll treat you to an amazing meal. Please?

141
00:20:02,075 --> 00:20:03,160
First,

142
00:20:03,243 --> 00:20:06,413
could you try this on for me?

143
00:20:06,496 --> 00:20:07,331
This.

144
00:20:07,414 --> 00:20:10,500
You can get changed over there.
If you can't manage, just holler.

145
00:20:12,377 --> 00:20:13,212
Okay.

146
