-You really have given up on everything.
-I have.

223
00:29:02,031 --> 00:29:05,952
I sleep all day,
eat whatever, and do nothing.

224
00:29:07,162 --> 00:29:08,246
So, do you feel smug?

225
00:29:09,456 --> 00:29:10,665
Watching us crash and burn?

226
00:29:12,333 --> 00:29:14,461
I thought I would, but not really.

227
00:29:15,503 --> 00:29:16,755
You should've done a better job.

228
00:29:18,214 --> 00:29:19,466
Tell me about it.

229
00:29:20,800 --> 00:29:23,094
I wish we could have shown you.

230
00:29:31,603 --> 00:29:33,730
About what you said, that you can't sing,

231
00:29:35,190 --> 00:29:36,232
I believe you.

232
00:29:39,486 --> 00:29:40,820
