233
00:29:44,073 --> 00:29:47,702
We may not have been friends,

234
00:29:48,995 --> 00:29:51,122
but we were at least comrades in arms.

235
00:29:53,124 --> 00:29:54,334
So I could tell.

236
00:29:56,377 --> 00:29:58,296
