237
00:29:59,422 --> 00:30:01,257
If you hadn't jumped off then,

238
00:30:02,675 --> 00:30:03,843
I probably would've myself.

239
00:30:10,099 --> 00:30:13,436
I don't hate you. You know that, right?

240
00:30:16,022 --> 00:30:18,566
I wanted to be like you, but I couldn't,

241
00:30:20,318 --> 00:30:22,403
and I didn't want to hate myself for it,

242
00:30:23,655 --> 00:30:25,740
so I think I hated you instead.

243
